@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zkadmf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (v0 * (wp.exp(v0 + 0.58) + tmp))
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.abs(0.60))
    v0 = wp.sin(v2)
    v1 = (wp.exp(wp.abs(tmp + 0.55)) + wp.sin((tmp + 0.42 + tmp + 0.22)))
    tmp = v0
    data[tid] = v0
